<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-19-0496 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper reports the use of the BASIC program to calculate the fieldstrength and homogeneity of the solenoid superconducting magnet, givingthe geometrical size of, and the wire needed for, the inner magnet inthe composite magnet system for the requirements of different field homogeneity.The fabrication technology and some measurements of the inner magnetmade of the multifilamentary Nb{sub 3}Sn composite conductor are givenin the example. They are applicable for the fabrication of the Nb{sub3}Sn superconducting magnet.</TEXT></DOC>